"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:45:41.000Z","msg":"Support<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc324da14d8f7298c7e40b6ef51104498cb8a81","tid":1849720,"uid":100871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:53:44.000Z","msg":"「你（政府）不封關，<span style=\"color: red;\">用全港公營醫療的資源，去處理一個國家的疫情</span>&hellip;&hellip;要醫護人員陪葬，我們怎可能接受？做醫護人員預計有可能受感染甚至死亡，但現在無掩雞籠、中門大開，我們實在是死得不明不白。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我就係要呢D"},{"pid":"61cfed12477e540de9bcf18d547da665bafe3084","tid":1849720,"uid":179703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e78a1467b3760fee2a9881ea63d3d96d885732b1","tid":1849720,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:51:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200129/s00001/1580283470720/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200129%2Fs00001%2F1580283470720%2F&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7Jo6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=9673634f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200129%2Fs00001%2F1580283470720%2F&h=de6f73cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200129/s00001/1580283470720/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200129/s00001/6248d988b974aca9a5b7133fb87b9c72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200129%2Fs00001%2F6248d988b974aca9a5b7133fb87b9c72.jpg&h=f09399ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新型冠狀病毒肺炎肆虐，多間公立醫院員工、醫護人員工會正醞釀罷工，抗議政府未有全面封關禁止內地人來港。本報獲悉，東區醫院手術室和博愛醫院手術室今日（29日）分別有27名和26名護士集體請病假，東區近半數手術室全日無護士上班。瑪嘉烈醫院一間內科病房亦再有最少3名護士請病假。有知情的醫護說：「你（政府）不封關，用全港公營醫療的資源，去處理一個國家的疫情&hellip;&hellip;要醫護人員陪葬，我們怎可能接受？做醫護人員預計有可能受感染甚至死亡，但現在無掩雞籠、中門大開，我們實在是死得不明不白。」本報正就事件向醫管局查詢。<br />\n<br />\n本報接獲公立醫院醫護人員消息稱，東區醫院手術室共有27名護士今日集體請病假。據悉，東區醫院共有12間手術室，另有8間預備和康復恢復室，本來編配了45名護士上班，請病假護士數目佔單日人手60%；有5間手術室全日無護士上班，佔近半數手術室。醫護消息指出，相信部分已預約的手術要推遲。另外，公立醫院醫護人員消息表示，博愛醫院今日亦有26名手術室護士集體請病假。<br />\n<br />\n瑪嘉烈醫院周一（27日）出現操普通話病人躺地拒隔離事件，據悉發生在內科F1病房。昨日內科F1和相鄰的E1病房已有大量護士集體請假，今日F1病房下午再有至少有3名護士請病假，剩兩名護士上班。<br />\n<br />\n有知情的醫護人員表示，請假護士主要抗議政府未有全面封關關禁內地人來港，「你不封關，用全港公營醫療的資源，去處理一個國家的疫情，人數無上限，政府無落力做針對的措施，要醫護人員陪葬，我們怎可能接受？做醫護人員預計有可能受感染甚至死亡，但現在無掩雞籠、中門大開，我們實在是死得不明不白，同事怨氣極大。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:56:38.000Z","msg":"三罷！"},{"pid":"b0bab76d908b36280675627c6f1df04d7f3f0c41","tid":1849720,"uid":67338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:57:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fccd1a5d6ccf5ae3d40c5ed7652f2a528296cdf3","tid":1849720,"uid":33357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:59:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2195aa22e7fbcee956c039c7dcd4ba87d1079c98","tid":1849720,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:01:21.000Z","msg":"Support and respect"},{"pid":"076a747bcee767ec177086143c273f6de09e3958","tid":1849720,"uid":172668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:02:21.000Z","msg":"支持醫護罷工"},{"pid":"566028c14b2